snippet: Woods’s agent, Mark Steinberg, confirmed in an email that Woods, who had hedged on his participation after missing the cut at the P.G.A. Championship, would play this week.
abstract: Tiger Woods, after missing cut at PGA Championship, will play Wyndham Championship for first time.
lead_paragraph: Woods’s agent, Mark Steinberg, confirmed in an email that Woods, who had hedged on his participation after missing the cut at the P.G.A. Championship, would play this week.

headline.main: Tiger Woods to Play Wyndham for First Time
